            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Judges.9:22-10:18",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJudges%209%3A22-10%3A18%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_22%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EShechem%20Rebels%20against%20Abimelech%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20Abimelech%20had%20ruled%20over%20Israel%20for%20three%20years%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_23%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EGod%20sent%20a%20spirit%20that%20stirred%20up%20trouble%20between%20Abimelech%20and%20the%20leading%20citizens%20of%20Shechem%2C%20and%20they%20revolted.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_24%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EGod%20was%20punishing%20Abimelech%20for%20murdering%20Gideon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20seventy%20sons%2C%20and%20the%20citizens%20of%20Shechem%20for%20supporting%20him%20in%20this%20treachery%20of%20murdering%20his%20brothers.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_25%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20citizens%20of%20Shechem%20set%20an%20ambush%20for%20Abimelech%20on%20the%20hilltops%20and%20robbed%20everyone%20who%20passed%20that%20way.%20But%20someone%20warned%20Abimelech%20about%20their%20plot.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_26%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20Gaal%20son%20of%20Ebed%20moved%20to%20Shechem%20with%20his%20brothers%20and%20gained%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20leading%20citizens%20of%20Shechem.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_27%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3EDuring%20the%20annual%20harvest%20festival%20at%20Shechem%2C%20held%20in%20the%20temple%20of%20the%20local%20god%2C%20the%20wine%20flowed%20freely%2C%20and%20everyone%20began%20cursing%20Abimelech.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_28%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWho%20is%20Abimelech%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20Gaal%20shouted.%20%26%23x201C%3BHe%26%23x2019%3Bs%20not%20a%20true%20son%20of%20Shechem%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A28%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EWho%20is%20Shechem%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20so%20why%20should%20we%20be%20his%20servants%3F%20He%26%23x2019%3Bs%20merely%20the%20son%20of%20Gideon%2C%20and%20this%20Zebul%20is%20merely%20his%20deputy.%20Serve%20the%20true%20sons%20of%20Hamor%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Shechem.%20Why%20should%20we%20serve%20Abimelech%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_29%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20I%20were%20in%20charge%20here%2C%20I%20would%20get%20rid%20of%20Abimelech.%20I%20would%20say%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A29%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3EAnd%20he%20said.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20him%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BGet%20some%20soldiers%2C%20and%20come%20out%20and%20fight!%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_30%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20when%20Zebul%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20city%2C%20heard%20what%20Gaal%20was%20saying%2C%20he%20was%20furious.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_31%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20sent%20messengers%20to%20Abimelech%20in%20Arumah%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A31%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ein%20secret%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Ein%20Tormah%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20compare%209%3A41.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20telling%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BGaal%20son%20of%20Ebed%20and%20his%20brothers%20have%20come%20to%20live%20in%20Shechem%2C%20and%20now%20they%20are%20inciting%20the%20city%20to%20rebel%20against%20you.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_32%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3ECome%20by%20night%20with%20an%20army%20and%20hide%20out%20in%20the%20fields.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_33%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20the%20morning%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20is%20daylight%2C%20attack%20the%20city.%20When%20Gaal%20and%20those%20who%20are%20with%20him%20come%20out%20against%20you%2C%20you%20can%20do%20with%20them%20as%20you%20wish.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_34%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Abimelech%20and%20all%20his%20men%20went%20by%20night%20and%20split%20into%20four%20groups%2C%20stationing%20themselves%20around%20Shechem.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_35%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3EGaal%20was%20standing%20at%20the%20city%20gates%20when%20Abimelech%20and%20his%20army%20came%20out%20of%20hiding.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_36%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Gaal%20saw%20them%2C%20he%20said%20to%20Zebul%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLook%2C%20there%20are%20people%20coming%20down%20from%20the%20hilltops!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EZebul%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%26%23x2019%3Bs%20just%20the%20shadows%20on%20the%20hills%20that%20look%20like%20men.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_37%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2237%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20again%20Gaal%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BNo%2C%20people%20are%20coming%20down%20from%20the%20hills.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A37a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20center%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20And%20another%20group%20is%20coming%20down%20the%20road%20past%20the%20Diviners%26%23x2019%3B%20Oak.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A37b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EElon-meonenim.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_38%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2238%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E38%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Zebul%20turned%20on%20him%20and%20asked%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BNow%20where%20is%20that%20big%20mouth%20of%20yours%3F%20Wasn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20it%20you%20that%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BWho%20is%20Abimelech%2C%20and%20why%20should%20we%20be%20his%20servants%3F%26%23x2019%3B%20The%20men%20you%20mocked%20are%20right%20outside%20the%20city!%20Go%20out%20and%20fight%20them!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_39%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2239%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E39%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Gaal%20led%20the%20leading%20citizens%20of%20Shechem%20into%20battle%20against%20Abimelech.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_40%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2240%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E40%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Abimelech%20chased%20him%2C%20and%20many%20of%20Shechem%26%23x2019%3Bs%20men%20were%20wounded%20and%20fell%20along%20the%20road%20as%20they%20retreated%20to%20the%20city%20gate.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_41%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2241%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E41%3C%2Fspan%3EAbimelech%20returned%20to%20Arumah%2C%20and%20Zebul%20drove%20Gaal%20and%20his%20brothers%20out%20of%20Shechem.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_42%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2242%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E42%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20next%20day%20the%20people%20of%20Shechem%20went%20out%20into%20the%20fields%20to%20battle.%20When%20Abimelech%20heard%20about%20it%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_43%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2243%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E43%3C%2Fspan%3Ehe%20divided%20his%20men%20into%20three%20groups%20and%20set%20an%20ambush%20in%20the%20fields.%20When%20Abimelech%20saw%20the%20people%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20city%2C%20he%20and%20his%20men%20jumped%20up%20from%20their%20hiding%20places%20and%20attacked%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_44%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2244%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E44%3C%2Fspan%3EAbimelech%20and%20his%20group%20stormed%20the%20city%20gate%20to%20keep%20the%20men%20of%20Shechem%20from%20getting%20back%20in%2C%20while%20Abimelech%26%23x2019%3Bs%20other%20two%20groups%20cut%20them%20down%20in%20the%20fields.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_45%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2245%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E45%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20battle%20went%20on%20all%20day%20before%20Abimelech%20finally%20captured%20the%20city.%20He%20killed%20the%20people%2C%20leveled%20the%20city%2C%20and%20scattered%20salt%20all%20over%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_46%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2246%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E46%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20leading%20citizens%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20tower%20of%20Shechem%20heard%20what%20had%20happened%2C%20they%20ran%20and%20hid%20in%20the%20temple%20of%20Baal-berith.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A46%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EEl-berith%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20another%20name%20for%20Baal-berith%3B%20compare%209%3A4.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_47%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2247%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E47%3C%2Fspan%3ESomeone%20reported%20to%20Abimelech%20that%20the%20citizens%20had%20gathered%20in%20the%20temple%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_48%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2248%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E48%3C%2Fspan%3Eso%20he%20led%20his%20forces%20to%20Mount%20Zalmon.%20He%20took%20an%20ax%20and%20chopped%20some%20branches%20from%20a%20tree%2C%20then%20put%20them%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20%26%23x201C%3BQuick%2C%20do%20as%20I%20have%20done!%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20told%20his%20men.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_49%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2249%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E49%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20each%20of%20them%20cut%20down%20some%20branches%2C%20following%20Abimelech%26%23x2019%3Bs%20example.%20They%20piled%20the%20branches%20against%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20temple%20and%20set%20them%20on%20fire.%20So%20all%20the%20people%20who%20had%20lived%20in%20the%20tower%20of%20Shechem%20died%26%23x2014%3Babout%201%2C000%20men%20and%20women.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_50%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2250%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E50%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Abimelech%20attacked%20the%20town%20of%20Thebez%20and%20captured%20it.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_51%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2251%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E51%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20tower%20inside%20the%20town%2C%20and%20all%20the%20men%20and%20women%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20entire%20population%26%23x2014%3Bfled%20to%20it.%20They%20barricaded%20themselves%20in%20and%20climbed%20up%20to%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20tower.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_52%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2252%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E52%3C%2Fspan%3EAbimelech%20followed%20them%20to%20attack%20the%20tower.%20But%20as%20he%20prepared%20to%20set%20fire%20to%20the%20entrance%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_53%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2253%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E53%3C%2Fspan%3Ea%20woman%20on%20the%20roof%20dropped%20a%20millstone%20that%20landed%20on%20Abimelech%26%23x2019%3Bs%20head%20and%20crushed%20his%20skull.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_54%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2254%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E54%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20quickly%20said%20to%20his%20young%20armor%20bearer%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BDraw%20your%20sword%20and%20kill%20me!%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20let%20it%20be%20said%20that%20a%20woman%20killed%20Abimelech!%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20the%20young%20man%20ran%20him%20through%20with%20his%20sword%2C%20and%20he%20died.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_55%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%225